c: 17
v: 64
t: Kamaba dumsoe nyang ek kamaba Mameh suara beu got kapeugah Kaparoh dum jih kalet ngon guda Ngon bala teuntra bala dum kakrah Kapeucharikat jih bak areuta Lom bak aneukda galak jih leupah Kajanji keu jih dum macam-macam Meu janji chetan bandum beurakah Cit tipee bandum meu janji chetan